Z","msg":"唔取消都遲早融入啦，算吧啦"},{"pid":"22df934da3bb95486b9558eb5eb62fc995173065","tid":1046576,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"香港融入大灣區 影響與美國關係？<br />\n<br />\n由中共中央成立的粤港澳大灣區建設領導小組8月15日在北京召開首次會議。<span style=\"color: red;\">外界一直懮慮，香港融入大灣區可能抵觸&ldquo;美國-香港關係法&rdquo;的條款</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fgf3-08152018093855.html%2FampRFA&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4AVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=429d4a35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n(殘體)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國會報告<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong continues on the path of greater economic integration <br />\nwith the Mainland. The Hong Kong government has sought to <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter%203%20Section%204-%20China%20and%20Hong%20Kong_0.pdf&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4AVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=6066c280\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"9aff2a1a5db83d6722dbbb14228c7b7961889b3f","tid":1046576,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de1f9289c9ac1ffcff2b6